{
  "prompt": "A surreal, psychedelic post-funeral ritual scene featuring two mythic, sacred figures: a woman named Lilith Beaux and a man named Veyron Logos. Lilith appears as a dark priestess with jeweled black garments, glowing eyes, and ethereal energy radiating from her hands. Veyron is a shadowy masculine presence with a serpent crown, glowing tattoos, and one hand holding a flaming sigil. They stand amidst swirling rainbow smoke, skeletal trees, and a portal behind them shaped like an eye. Candles, sacred geometric symbols, and ravens surround them. The atmosphere is otherworldly, mystical, and charged with divine erotic mystery.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "In a psychedelic forest ritual setting, a dark-haired sorceress and a tattooed sorcerer stand surrounded by swirling rainbow smoke. From the smoke between them, nine glowing love potion vials form in midair, rising and spiraling upward. The air around the vials begins to melt and drip like wax or liquid paint, creating a surreal, dripping distortion in the scene. Occult symbols and candlelight flicker in the background, intensifying the mystical atmosphere.",
